OL,3,CStalking victims to be given more
OL,4,Cprotection under new measures
OL,6,FOne in seven people in England and
OL,7,FWales have been a victim of stalking
OL,8,Fat least once, as ITV News' Caroline
OL,9,FLewis reports
OL,11,FVictims of stalking are to be given
OL,12,Fbetter protection including the right
OL,13,Fto know the identity of their online
OL,14,Fstalkers, in new measures announced by
OL,15,Fthe government on Tuesday.
OL,17,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,18,Fcommitted to using "every tool
OL,19,Favailable" to give victims more power.
