OL,3,CStalking victims to be given more
OL,4,Cprotection under new measures
OL,6,FThe changes come following a warning
OL,7,Fearlier this year from a group of
OL,8,Fwatchdogs who said police are failing
OL,9,Fto protect stalking victims in too
OL,10,Fmany cases.
OL,12,FNew "right to know" statutory guidance
OL,13,Fwill "empower" the police to tell
OL,14,Fvictims of an online stalker's
OL,15,Fidentity at the earliest opportunity,
OL,16,Fthe Home Office said.
OL,18,FThe new guidance was inspired by
OL,19,Fformer Coronation Street actress and
OL,20,FTalk TV host Nicola Thorp, who was a
OL,21,Fvictim of stalking and online abuse.
