OL,3,CStalking victims to be given more
OL,4,Cprotection under new measures
OL,6,FMs Thorp was stalked and abused online
OL,7,Ffor months by a man who set up almost
OL,8,F30 social media accounts to send her
OL,9,Fviolent misogynistic messages.
OL,11,FPolice said they could not reveal the
OL,12,Fidentity of the offender even after he
OL,13,Fwas arrested.
OL,15,FMs Thorp only learned his true
OL,16,Fidentity when his 30-month prison
OL,17,Fsentence and lifetime restraining
OL,18,Forder was handed down in court.
