OL,3,CStalking victims to be given more
OL,4,Cprotection under new measures
OL,6,F"For too long, stalking victims have
OL,7,Fbeen at the mercy not only of their
OL,8,Fstalker, but a justice system that
OL,9,Ffailed to protect them," she said.
OL,11,F"These new measures will empower
OL,12,Fvictims to regain some much-needed
OL,13,Fcontrol of their lives and police to
OL,14,Fbring abusers to justice."
OL,16,FOther measures announced by the Home
OL,17,FOffice include Stalking Protection
OL,18,FOrders ` which can ban stalkers from
OL,19,Fgoing within a certain distance of
OL,20,Ftheir victims, or contacting them `
OL,21,Fbeing made more widely available.
