OL,3,CStalking victims to be given more
OL,4,Cprotection under new measures
OL,6,FThe new approach will see courts able
OL,7,Fto impose such orders after a
OL,8,Fconviction even where none was in
OL,9,Fplace before a trial, contrary to the
OL,10,Fcurrent process where one has to have
OL,11,Fbeen in place already.
OL,13,FThis will stop offenders from
OL,14,Fcontacting their victims from prison,
OL,15,Fthe department said.
