OL,3,CStalking victims to be given more
OL,4,Cprotection under new measures
OL,6,FOther changes include defining
OL,7,Fstalking in statutory guidance and
OL,8,Fsetting out a framework in law to help
OL,9,Fsupport services work together to
OL,10,Fensure no-one is failed by vital
OL,11,Finformation falling through the cracks.
OL,13,FThe Home Office said it will publish
OL,14,Fnew data on stalking offences to
OL,15,Finform policy and policing decisions,
OL,16,Fand set out national standards on
OL,17,Fstalking perpetrator programmes to
OL,18,Fensure consistency across England and
OL,19,FWales.
