OL,3,CStalking victims to be given more
OL,4,Cprotection under new measures
OL,6,F"This starts with empowering police to
OL,7,Fgive women the right to know the
OL,8,Fidentity of their online stalkers,
OL,9,Fstrengthening stalking protection
OL,10,Forders and ensuring that the police
OL,11,Fwork with all support services to give
OL,12,Fvictims the protection they deserve."
OL,14,FThe government has also committed to
OL,15,Faccepting or partially accepting all
OL,16,Fof the recommendations launched in
OL,17,Fresponse to a so-called super-
OL,18,Fcomplaint raised two years ago by the
OL,19,FSuzy Lamplugh Trust on behalf of the
OL,20,FNational Stalking Consortium.
