OL,4,Cprotection under new measures
OL,6,FThe complaint set out concerns
OL,7,Fincluding how there had been flawed
OL,8,Finvestigations, instances where
OL,9,Fstalking was not being properly
OL,10,Fidentified, officers "minimising or
OL,11,Ftrivialising" such behaviour and the
OL,12,Frisk of victims being seriously hurt
OL,13,For killed not being recognised.
